text: Deborah Cox (July 13, 1974, Toronto) is a Canadian singer, songwriter and actress who has had eleven charting #1 singles. She has had some hit movies, such as Love Come Down. She began her music career around the mid 1990s. Her song "Nobody's Supposed to be Here" is her signature song.
